<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Lefebvre, N. and Schelein, M., "The Liar Lied," in <a href="/wiki/Philosophy_Now" title="Philosophy Now">Philosophy Now</a> issue 51</li>
</ol>
